            "text": "<p>Browse the collection above for handcarved fairies, woodland animals, Romanian folk figures, mushrooms, and miniature playscape pieces. Whether you are building a fairy garden, a Waldorf nature table, or a small-world play setup, Bumbu Toys bring quiet folk-art charm to every story.</p>"
